                                "editor": "<p>All payments are processed securely through <a href=\"https:\/\/www.lemonsqueezy.com\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-fpl-component=\"primitive\">lemonsqueezy.com<\/a>. Simplly does not directly process payments through the website. Feel free to contact us about our security policies.<\/p>",
