                                "editor": "<p>We, at Simplly stand by our products and believe that they are the best possible solutions we deliver. However, if you come across any issues or incompatibilities, you can open up a ticket at our support center and allow us to help you resolve your issue. Dedicated support is promised to only those who possess an active license. Free versions are not promised for instant support.<\/p>",
